room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Unity Escape Rooms in Redlands
room_address: 2015 W Park Ave Suite 2B Redlands, CA 92373
room_description: You are forced to take an unexpected trip into the woods to look for your friend – a journalist who was trying to solve the mystery of an old house where, if you believe in legends, some black magic was practiced. His last message was quite disturbing, and it looks like you have very little time if you want to see him alive again…
